node.text:
@Ramtin_Ray_Nosrati ‘s $44,000,000 latest masterpiece with its own man cave that offers a 20 car garage. This stunning gated home is approximately 18,000 sqft and sits on 1.5 acres with its own private security booth, custom built helicopter with TV & lounge inside, basketball court, indoor and outdoor pool w/spa, sports simulator room, barber shop & salon along with stunning views of Los Angeles and much more. Tag someone you would stay here with!
